reviewText: It's a funny film. I had it at one point and lost the movie so I bought it again. In one word awesome.

Lorena Alvarez is the star of this movie, she's ok to look at , but she's not that funny.  It has english subtitles.  The plot is really dumb, but it's less than 90 mins.  There are a couple of ironic twists in end.  There's one funny scene,at the end of the movie.  I don't know what country it takes place in.  Lorena Alvarez should be in a novela instead.
